support: .icon-support{box-sizing:border-box;position:relative;display:block;width:20px;height:20px;transform:rotate(45deg) scale(var(--tw-icon,1));border:5px solid transparent;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px,inset 0 0 0 2px;border-radius:40px}.icon-support::after,.icon-support::before{content:"";display:block;box-sizing:border-box;position:absolute}.icon-support::before{border-left:9px solid;border-right:9px solid;width:24px;height:2px;left:-7px;top:4px}.icon-support::after{width:2px;height:24px;border-top:9px solid;border-bottom:9px solid;left:4px;top:-7px}
tikcode: .icon-tikcode{box-sizing:border-box;position:relative;display:block;transform:scale(var(--tw-icon,1));width:18px;height:18px;background:linear-gradient(to left,currentColor 10px,transparent 0) no-repeat 10px 0/8px 2px,linear-gradient(to left,currentColor 10px,transparent 0) no-repeat 10px 6px/8px 2px,linear-gradient(to left,currentColor 10px,transparent 0) no-repeat 10px 10px/2px 8px,linear-gradient(to left,currentColor 10px,transparent 0) no-repeat 13px 10px/2px 8px,linear-gradient(to left,currentColor 10px,transparent 0) no-repeat 16px 10px/2px 8px,linear-gradient(to left,currentColor 10px,transparent 0) no-repeat 16px 0/2px 8px,linear-gradient(to left,currentColor 10px,transparent 0) no-repeat 10px 0/2px 8px}.icon-tikcode::after,.icon-tikcode::before{content:"";position:absolute;display:block;box-sizing:border-box;width:8px;height:8px;border:2px solid}.icon-tikcode::after{bottom:0}
trees: .icon-trees{box-sizing:border-box;position:relative;display:block;transform:scale(var(--tw-icon,1));width:16px;height:20px;border-left:4px solid transparent;border-right:3px solid transparent;border-top:10px solid transparent;box-shadow:inset 2px 0 0,inset -2px 0 0}.icon-trees::after,.icon-trees::before{content:"";display:block;position:absolute;box-sizing:border-box;width:10px;height:16px;border:2px solid;border-radius:8px;left:-4px;top:-10px}.icon-trees::after{width:8px;height:12px;top:-6px;left:4px}
trending-down: .icon-trending-down{box-sizing:border-box;position:relative;display:block;transform:rotate(45deg) scale(var(--tw-icon,1));width:10px;height:8px;border-bottom:2px solid;border-right:2px solid}.icon-trending-down::after,.icon-trending-down::before{content:"";display:block;box-sizing:border-box;position:absolute}.icon-trending-down::before{background:currentColor;left:8px;width:10px;height:2px;top:0}.icon-trending-down::after{width:0;height:0;border-top:4px solid transparent;border-bottom:4px solid transparent;border-left:6px solid;top:-3px;right:-14px}
trending: .icon-trending{box-sizing:border-box;position:relative;display:block;transform:rotate(-45deg) scale(var(--tw-icon,1));width:10px;height:8px;border-top:2px solid;border-right:2px solid}.icon-trending::after,.icon-trending::before{content:"";display:block;box-sizing:border-box;position:absolute}.icon-trending::before{background:currentColor;left:8px;width:10px;height:2px;bottom:0}.icon-trending::after{width:0;height:0;border-top:4px solid transparent;border-bottom:4px solid transparent;border-left:6px solid;bottom:-3px;right:-14px}
usb: .icon-usb,.icon-usb::before{display:block;box-sizing:border-box}.icon-usb{position:relative;width:14px;height:14px;border:2px solid;transform:scale(var(--tw-icon,1));margin-bottom:-6px;border-bottom-left-radius:3px;border-bottom-right-radius:3px}.icon-usb::before{content:"";position:absolute;width:6px;height:5px;border-left:1px solid transparent;border-right:1px solid transparent;border-top:1px solid transparent;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px,inset 5px 4px 0 -4px,inset -5px 4px 0 -4px;top:-7px;left:2px}
youtube: .icon-youtube{box-sizing:border-box;position:relative;display:block;transform:scale(var(--tw-icon,1));width:16px;height:10px;box-shadow:0 0 0 2px;border-radius:15px 15px 15px 15px /45px 45px 45px 45px}.icon-youtube::before{content:"";display:block;box-sizing:border-box;position:absolute;left:7px;top:2px;border-left:4px solid currentColor;border-top:3px solid transparent;border-bottom:3px solid transparent}
zeit: .icon-zeit{box-sizing:border-box;position:relative;display:block;transform:scale(var(--tw-icon,1));width:0px;height:0px;border-left:9px solid transparent;border-right:9px solid transparent;border-bottom:18px solid currentColor;}
